<title>Syncronization</title>
<para>This module privides the core synchronization facilites for K42.</para>
  <ItemizedList spacing="compact">
    <listitem>
      <simpara>
	<ulink url="&topsrc/lib/libc/sync/Lock.H">Lock.H</ulink> 

	The basic blocking locks are available by including this file.
	It is automatically included from <ulink
	url="&topsrc/lib/libc/sync/../sys/sysIncs.H">sys/sysIncs.H</ulink>.  We define
	here ous generic machinary for locking, including the
	structure for a lock embedded in the bottom bits of a pointer,
	and the "AutoLock" facility which allows locks to be
	automatically acquired and released on entry to a facility.

      </simpara>
